  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we thought about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I consciously thought about it quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You must understand, all of us, reacted after the war, according to his capability.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The camp, in the end, was only a [? katalysator ?] for what each of us had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The experience could wind up quicker the potentiality in us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Many of us wanted to run away, never hear about it or broke all the contact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Others wanted to throw themselves into the daily life, to make money, or to achieve something in  the scientific field, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My desire was I knew it clearly, I must--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in the world of children, I want to express what happened to a Jewish child in the war, the suffering.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started years after the war, to draw only Muselmann and suffering of children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never brutal, but the sadness, the loneliness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I thought, in my naive way, if I will tell them after the war, what happened to us, people will change for better.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the greatest disappointed was that nobody wanted to listen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not in Czechoslovakia, not in Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Israel they started to tell us, oh well, we had it all so bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got only half a loaf of this, and only one--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only two, three eggs in a week, to me, who just came from the camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And something similar, not like--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We shut up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we spoke only between us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we saw from the reactions, that people didn't want to hear it in Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only after the Eichmann trial, things changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They needed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I called it, they always used us like clothes you took from naphthalene.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
